### ============================================================
### ClickUp Reporting API — Local Development Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000 (sam local start-api)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = local-dev-api-key-12345

### ============================================================
### Manual Trigger — Generate Daily Report
### ============================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "report_type": "daily",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "period_end": "2025-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}

