### ============================================================
### Backfill — Generate Reports for a Date Range
### ============================================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/backfill
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "from_date": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "to_date": "2025-01-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### ============================================================
### Error Cases
### ============================================================

### Missing API key — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "report_type": "daily",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "period_end": "2025-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}

### Invalid API key — expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: wrong-key

{
  "report_type": "daily",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "period_end": "2025-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}

### Missing request body — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Invalid report_type — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "report_type": "yearly",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "period_end": "2025-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}

### Missing period_end — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "report_type": "daily",
  "period_start": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### period_start after period_end — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "report_type": "daily",
  "period_start": "2025-01-10T00:00:00Z",
  "period_end": "2025-01-01T23:59:59Z"
}

### Backfill — missing from_date — expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/reports/backfill
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "to_date": "2025-01-31T23:59:59Z"
}
